Currently all annotations are of type rdf:type a:Annotation (namespace a=http://www.w3.org/2000/10/annotation-ns#). 
They typically also have a more specific annotation subclass type e.g. rdf:type aT:Comment (namespace aT =http://www.w3.org/2000/10/annotationType#). 
It is also possible for a group to define other annotation subtypes and use them. 
The a:Annotation could naturally be left out and just infer it from the more specific type by using the knowledge about subClassOf definition between the types. 
We have not currently done it for couple of reasons related to history and optimization. 
